<li><ruby style="ruby-align: center; font-size: x-small;" lang="zh"><rb><span class="largeChinese" style="font-size: large;">吗／嗎</span></rb><rp>(</rp><rt class="pinyin" style="font-family:'Arial Unicode MS', 'Bitstream Cyberbit', 'TITUS Cyberbit Basic', 'Lucida Sans Unicode'; font-family &#160;:inherit;"><span style="font-size: x-small;font-family:'Arial Unicode MS', 'Arial';"><span title="ISO 7098 Chinese" class="Unicode" style="white-space:normal; text-decoration: none">ma</span></span></rt><rp>)</rp></ruby> "question particle"—<b>neutral</b></li>
</ul>
<table class="metadata mbox-small" style="border:1px solid #aaa; background-color:#f9f9f9;">
<tr>
